title: Greens Up! - Montana Avenue
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Organic, Salad bar, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Salad bar restaurant offering quick salads made with fresh local ingredients, including some organic, and in-house dressings. The Thai salad is vegan, or build your own salad. Also offers a muddling bar with farmers market fruit and herbs to be mashed into organic ice tea and lemonade. Bags and cups are made from plants and are biodegradable. Has Wi-Fi.
